results.description:
INSTANT DOWNLOAD | NO PHYSICAL PRINT INCLUDED

You are purchasing an Instant Download of my original design.

Print out this original, modern artwork for your home, studio or office! 

Your order includes (4) high-quality JPEG files in 2X3, 3X4, 4X5 and ISO (A1, A2, A3, etc...) ratio sizes. This means you can print multiple sizes and dimensions as many times as you like up to a massive 24X36"! 

File 1: 2X3 RATIO - 4"x6", 8"X12", 12"X18", 16"X24", 20"X30", and 24"X36"

File 2: 3X4 RATIO - 6"X8", 9"X12", 12"X16", 15"X20", 18"X24"

File 3: 4X5 RATIO - 4"X5", 8"X10", 11"X14", 12"X15", 16"X20"

File 4: ISO (International Standard) RATIO: A1, A2, A3, A4, A5, and 5"X7"

Your artwork is ready to print at 300dpi in RGB color format, ensuring a clear, crisp image that will look gorgeous adorning whatever space you choose to display it in!

There are 3 main ways to print:

- At your home or office
- Send the files to your local Print Shop, such as Staples, Kinko's, Target, etc...
- Print using an online service such as Shutterfly, Mpix, or Finerworks.

Please note that color appearance varies based on different brands of monitors, and final print quality will depend on the calibre of printer and paper used. I recommend using an online service and a heavier gram of paper for optimum results. Please make sure you choose a frame/matting that fits your new artwork!

After purchase, you can access your files here:
http://www.etsy.com/your/purchases

Your files will be automatically available on the "purchases" page of your account once your payment has cleared with Etsy. The mobile/tablet app doesn't allow downloading, but you can access your files on your mobile device's browser in: Etsy > You > Purchases and Reviews.
